package testchain

// erc1155BytecodeHex is the creation bytecode for the minimal test ERC-1155
// (TestNFT1155): ERC-165 supportsInterface (0x01ffc9a7 + 0xd9b67a26),
// balanceOf(owner,id), a public mint(to,id,amount), and the canonical
// safeTransferFrom(from,to,id,amount,data) (0xf242432a). It omits operators/batch
// and the receiver callback — the smallest contract that passes ERC-165 1155
// detection and moves a balance for a real on-chain assertion. Compiled offline
// with solc 0.8.26 (optimizer on) from src/TestNFT1155.sol and checked in so the
// integration test needs no solc at run time. See erc1155.go for the deploy +
// raw-RPC reader.
const erc1155BytecodeHex = ""
